@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    /* Custom styles for Privacy Policy */
    .privacy-container {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-bottom: 50px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .privacy-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-content {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

        .privacy-content h4 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-content p,
        .privacy-content ul {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .privacy-content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .privacy-content a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .privacy-content a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

    .form-row-last {
        margin-top: 30px;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .privacy-title {
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .privacy-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }

            .privacy-content h4 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .privacy-content p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .privacy-content ul {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

        .form-row-last {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 576px) {
        .privacy-title {
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .privacy-content {
            padding: 10px;
        }

            .privacy-content h4 {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .privacy-content p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .privacy-content ul {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

        .form-row-last {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    }

</style>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h2>

        <div class="privacy-content">
            <h4>Introduction</h4>
            <p>
                We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our ChatBot application.
            </p>

            <h4>Information We Collect</h4>
            <p>
                We may collect personal data such as your name, email address, phone number, and other information you provide during your interaction with our ChatBot. Additionally, we collect usage data to improve the services we provide.
            </p>

            <h4>How We Use Your Information</h4>
            <p>
                The information we collect may be used for the following purposes:
                <ul>
                    <li>To provide personalized responses from our ChatBot.</li>
                    <li>To improve the accuracy and efficiency of our AI algorithms.</li>
                    <li>To contact you regarding updates or changes to our services.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>

            <h4>Data Retention</h4>
            <p>
                We retain your information only for as long as necessary to provide the services you have requested. We will delete your personal data when it is no longer needed for these purposes or if you request that we do so.
            </p>

            <h4>Data Security</h4>
            <p>
                We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>

            <h4>Third-Party Services</h4>
            <p>
                We may share your data with third-party service providers who assist us in running the ChatBot application. These third parties are obligated to protect your data and may only use it for the services we provide.
            </p>

            <h4>Your Rights</h4>
            <p>
                You have the right to:
                <ul>
                    <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you.</li>
                    <li>Request correction of any inaccurate data.</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal requirements).</li>
                </ul>
            </p>

            <h4>Cookies</h4>
            <p>
                We may use cookies to enhance your experience and collect usage data. Cookies are small files stored on your device that help us improve the application’s functionality and performance.
            </p>

            <h4>Changes to Privacy Policy</h4>
            <p>
                We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the revised date will be indicated at the top of the page.
            </p>

            <h4>Contact Us</h4>
            <p>
                If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@apnaai.com.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
